These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, turtle, lizard, hamster, dog, pony
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the pony##2
 2. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
10. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Pet   | lizard | goldfish | pony | mouse    | turtle | hamster   | dog    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, grapefruit, grapes, lettuce, pomegranate, pumpkin
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, tram, bus, train, taxi, car, ship
1. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating pomegranate and the person driving the car##2
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person driving the train##1
9. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | lettuce | grapefruit | pomegranate | cauliflower | pumpkin | apple      | grapes  |
| Transport   | car | train  | ship     | bus     | taxi  | bike | tram |

