.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german, indian, mexican, pakistani, polish
There 7 different types of food: eggplant, grapefruit, cauliflower, apple, peach, pear, artichoke
 1. the mexican is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 3. the person eating peach is the polish##1
 4. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 6. the indian is the person eating apple##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person eating eggplant is between the person eating artichoke and the indian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person eating pear##1
10. the dutch is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | canadian | dutch   | indian | german | pakistani |
| Food           | peach | pear     | grapefruit     | cauliflower | apple   | eggplant   | artichoke    |

