.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, june, november, april, october, february, may
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, polish
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the mexican is between the person who's birthday is in november and the pakistani##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
 8. the mexican is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is the chinese##1
10. the australian is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Birthday      | november    | october  | april  | july  | may      | february       | june |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | pakistani | polish | australian | malaysian | chinese  |

