.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, disco, folk, house, metal, punk, rock
There are 7 different favourite colors: purple, turquise, grey, chestnut, coral, blue, azure
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who likes coral is the fan of disco##1
3. the person who likes purple is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
5. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
6. the person who likes blue is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
8. the person who likes turquise is the fan of house##1
9. the fan of metal is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | metal | classical | folk | rock      | disco      | punk |
| Color     | turquise | blue | azure       | purple | grey | coral | chestnut |

