5. the videographer is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to prague and the firefighter##2
7. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the videographer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
