.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: december, september, august, january, february, july, november
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard, taxi, tram, trike
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Birthday   | september | january     | july | february | august | november  | december |
