5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who likes grey is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who likes coral##2
7. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes amber and the person who likes emerald##2
8. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
