 3. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 4. the person watching western movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching spy movies##2
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
