 3. the person drinking sprite is between the game-smoker and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking mirinda##2
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
