 8. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
